  "description": "A long exposure night photograph showcases a vibrant cityscape and bridge illuminated with lights, culminating in a spectacular fireworks display. The foreground features a long, modern bridge with glowing white lights stretching across dark water. Beyond the bridge, a sprawling city skyline rises, densely packed with illuminated buildings of varying heights. A large, multi-tiered burst of fireworks explodes in the center of the frame, adding a dramatic and colorful element to the scene. The overall effect is a captivating blend of urban architecture, modern infrastructure, and celebratory pyrotechnics.",
